---
title: Lamb & Spinach Shepherd's Pie with Creamy Chive Mash
description: Did you know that shepherd’s pie traditionally uses lamb, while cottage pie uses beef? We kept up with tradition in this winter
warmer, but decided to make our version extra-nutritious by stirring baby spinach through the hearty lamb filling. Enjoy the
a comforting mix of old and new!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
